============================================================================

SPIRIT-AI NANO-GPT CONFIGURATION (RTX 5090 Optimized)

============================================================================

DIRECTORIES

DATA_DIR=/workspace/data
OUTPUT_DIR=/workspace/models

HYPERPARAMETERS - Training

Lowered Batch Size to 8 to prevent OOM errors on the 5090

BATCH_SIZE=8
BLOCK_SIZE=256
MAX_ITERS=100000
EVAL_INTERVAL=500
LEARNING_RATE=3e-4

HYPERPARAMETERS - Model Architecture

n_embd 384 + 12 layers is the "stability sweet spot"

N_EMBD=384
N_HEAD=8
N_LAYER=12

GENERATION

MAX_NEW_TOKENS=100
